==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pou sto
<hw>Pou sto</hw> <pr>(p⟦oomac⟧ st⟦omac⟧; pou st⟦omac⟧)</pr>.
<ety>[Gr. <grk>poy^ stw^</grk> where I may stand; -- from the reputed
saying of Archimedes, ⟦ldquo⟧Give me where I may stand and I will move
the whole world with my steelyard.⟦rdquo⟧]</ety> <def>A place to stand
upon; a locus standi; hence, a foundation or basis for
operations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pout</ent>⟦br⟧
